.pl 30 ;saving paper
.ds .1st.first.
.ds .2nd.second.
.ds .all.\1st\ \2nd\.
.ds .ALL.\\1st\\ \\2nd\\.
=\all\
=\ALL\
=\all\
=\ALL\
